Package nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord

package nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord
Discord bot implementation using this commands system.
Main classes to pay attention to:
  • DiscordBot An example of an implemented bot class with the command system.
  • DiscordCenter The command center which is attached to the main class of a plugin.
  • DiscordUser A user implementation with functions to send messages and derivatives to a Discord user.
  • nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord.extensions Extensions to the parameter parsing and context handling
Since:
v0.1
